-- Ferguson Says Recommendations on Australia Mining Tax May Come By December
-- B y   M a r i o n   R a e
-- 2010-09-21T05:45:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-21/ferguson-says-recommendations-on-australia-mining-tax-may-come-by-december.html
Australia’s mining tax will have
“key recommendations” on its final design put to the
government in mid-December after talks with industry in the
coming months, Australian Resources Minister Martin Ferguson
told ABC24 television today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Marion Rae in Canberra at 
 mrae3@bloomberg.net  